thread.title: Who Needs a Down Payment? Trade In Your Old Home Instead

author: Laura Kusisto
title: Who Needs a Down Payment? Trade In Your Old Home Instead
text:
Soon it may be nearly as easy to trade in an old home for a new one as it is to dispense with a used car.
Open Door Labs Inc., a San Francisco startup that buys homes in cash and turns around and flips them, is getting into business with home builders. The partnerships will offer new-home buyers a “trade-in” feature that will allow them to...
